structure.unit: GENERAL PROVISIONS AS TO OFFICES AND OFFICERS -- SOCIAL SECURITY FOR PUBLIC EMPLOYEES -- EMPLOYEES RETIREMENT SYSTEM

law.history: Repealed 1966 Ky. Acts ch. 32, sec. 7; and ch. 255, sec. 283. -- Amended 1954 Ky. Acts ch. 84, sec. 1. -- Created 1946 Ky. Acts ch. 144, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Reinstatement of War Veterans in public position or employment held before entering service.
